list.name: Changes
list.comment: Updated turns with modifiers, production, and trade routes Updated province command to reflect trade good change Added tech and researching commands Added modifiers to registration Added multiple new QOL commands for mods and devs Updated bank command with new calculations and view Updated recruit command with added troop costs based on level Updated mass recruit command with added troop costs based on level Updated construct command with Workshops and Temples Added visual thousands commas for the construct command Updated deconstruction command with Workshops and Temples Added visual trade good market command Updated combat with army levels, terrain modifiers, and rounds Added cnc_locate to display a specified province Refactored for optimization Updated register with new options, requiring a focus, and auto-assigning a blank province Removed cnc_purchase in favor of future colonization
